&lt;p&gt;PMC&#39;s comprehensive benefits package is thoughtfully designed to support every aspect of your life, empowering you to thrive both personally and professionally. &lt;strong&gt;We offer PMC-Paid Healthcare with&amp;nbsp;no employee paycheck contributions on medical, dental, and vision for you and your family.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;PMC also offers&amp;nbsp;Flexible Spending Accounts (Healthcare, Dependent Care &amp;amp; Commuter), an Employee Assistance Program, Lif

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fairchild: Digital Director&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fairchild is home to iconic brands including Women’s Wear Daily (WWD),&amp;nbsp;Footwear News (FN), and Beauty Inc,&amp;nbsp;and sits at the center of the global fashion, beauty, and retail industries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated and detail-oriented Digital Director to lead a team of digital writers, identifying breaking news, trending stories, and cultural moments, and assign content swiftly and accordingly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities will include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead a team of digital writers plus freelancers and foster a collaborative, ambitious and ideas-driven culture for WWD, Beauty Inc and Footwear News&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assign, edit, and write digital content across the site, ensuring accuracy, voice consistency, and editorial quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and regularly update the editorial calendar, balancing timely content with evergreen priorities while ensuring team meets deadlines and traffic goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate and collaborate with the Eye team on coverage of red carpet and celebrities and the Fashion team on style and trends, creating synergy and avoiding duplication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With the senior editorial team, design and develop the publication’s SEO strategy, including keyword research, headline optimization, evergreen content planning, and performance tracking, and execute accordingly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with&amp;nbsp;editors and writers across the organization to ensure best and consistent SEO practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor, analyze and report on traffic trends, search performance, and audience behavior to inform content decisions; create internal reporting system and decks to present to senior-level staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pitch, package, and optimize stories for Apple News and other distribution or syndication partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with depts for tentpoles, big initiatives, business-related events, and special projects and create a content plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a point-person for web needs for staff members, and monitor user experience for the reader, working closely with the Product team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure content meets legal, ethical, and fact-checking standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least five years of digital news experience at a media outlet with a deep understanding of what resonates online&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Someone who is chronically online and can identify an emerging shift in consumer behavior and use of language, what topics are gaining traction and identify rising talent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong vision, sharp editorial eye, clear communicator who is comfortable speaking in front of staff members and approaching and collaborating with senior-level editors across the publication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Culturally in-tune, able to identify the nuance of each bureau, department and beat and communicate accordingly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with interests and needs of the Fairchild publication trade and consumer reader&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proven track record of managing a team and collaborating with other departments across multiple platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong understanding of audience analytics; familiarity with digital subscriptions a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An elastic mindset that is in tune with the industry, current affairs and the needs of an evolving newsroom&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
