&lt;p&gt;Penske Media Corporation (PMC), the parent company of Rolling Stone, Variety, Billboard, The Hollywood Reporter, SXSW, The Golden Globes, and many more brands, is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Day Porter&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Facilities team in our New York office. This is an integral role on a service-oriented team proud of keeping our workplace safe, clean, and welcoming for all employees and guests. We value collaboration, people-first service, and the ability to proactively anticipate needs.&lt;/p&gt;
