&lt;li&gt;Establish and follow standards for how data is organized, documented, and used across the data warehouse&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement data quality checks, validation frameworks, and monitoring to ensure reliability of critical datasets&lt;/li&gt;
